{"tid":377512,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有個日本地方細個去過好想去番","createTime":"2017-08-27T17:49:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T01:43:27.000Z","uid":101024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"947d40b24337f90308d4f177defc243ee1a31275","tid":377512,"uid":101024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T17:49:29.000Z","msg":"記得果時係由和歌山白濱附近回程番大阪、途中經過一個唔知叫咩咩湖既地方，個導遊好似話係拍拖勝地好浪漫咁樣。<br />\n<br />\n我真係好想去番，搵左好耐都搵唔到 所以希望係度集思廣益一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e07d122838b33525caa080e402a6d3e1ee0b0746","tid":377512,"uid":101024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T05:18:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cacba5746643c226fa6e6d1e37402a5412bbd319","tid":377512,"uid":134933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T05:21:21.000Z","msg":"洞爺湖"},{"pid":"0385c6c9b0dddc9aa5a9a6d47763509f380f1497","tid":377512,"uid":129378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T05:44:15.000Z","msg":"有無多少少資料？<br />\n近白濱？和歌山？大阪？<br />\n<br />\n不過呢頭都無乜大湖出名"},{"pid":"ae02af4176244adbe74677de5a43438fa3aae162","tid":377512,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T05:54:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洞爺湖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主話白濱喎"},{"pid":"2aa348af5a778e4e58b9bd23e06a47d02baa48ba","tid":377512,"uid":49203,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T06:50:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洞爺湖</blockquote><br />\n和歌山番大阪經北海道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8db787341a07c27ceaa987a7990387f40a12a6","tid":377512,"uid":73374,"like":0,"dislike":