ji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多地方都係咁wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我記得好似係去完白濱坐旅遊巴番大阪時 導遊話番去前去埋果個地方，所以應該係比較近大阪既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c646a3ce2484d409c95e8dafa60b91dd7fb1413f","tid":377512,"uid":92201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T01:43:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://seichi.net/gotoseichi/detail.php?l_id=264\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fseichi.net%2Fgotoseichi%2Fdetail.php%3Fl_id%3D264&d=45QK8%2BHIcQDXOtE2NZYarfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=42ced488\" target=\"_blank\">http://seichi.net/gotoseichi/detail.php?l_id=264</a><br />\n<br />\ngoogle search 和歌山 恋人の聖地"}]}